title: Breaking Down the Rudy Gobert Trade and Day 2 of Free Agency
description:
Logan and Rob start by discussing the Rudy Gobert trade and what it means for both the Timberwolves and the Jazz (1:36). Then, they talk about Malcolm Brogdon going to the Celtics (16:18), before breaking down some of the rest of the big stories from Day 2 of free agency (21:15).

Hosts: Logan Murdock and Rob Mahoney
Associate Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
